{"tid":1945504,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"發生咗件好不愉快的事","createTime":"2020-03-27T06:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T06:31:43.000Z","uid":345989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0686563c48b5812f1b7a2781774f3ef56305b5","tid":1945504,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱去超市買嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揀緊貨品嗰陣時見到有個人架車啲嘢跌晒落地下<br />\n<br />\n我好心去幫佢執返<br />\n<br />\n但係嗰個阿嬸見到我幫佢執嘢<br />\n<br />\n佢即刻叫我走開，話唔使我幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n驚我有病菌<br />\n<br />\n雖然我理解佢都唔係特登<br />\n<br />\n但係真係好hurt我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a82a3a708f6e6941c2d79d9703f26e161eadd14","tid":1945504,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8729b7f5a992538fe927097d5cbe84588fdbbb4f","tid":1945504,"uid":134268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb58a4a05473cfa71f0eb3e3467540aa5a64432","tid":1945504,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3318483f44f3a957bf1fd9c08fc518875a51d76","tid":1945504,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"唔使你幫又點hunt到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b191790256ac7752221bdfc95c24a6a13e972fc7","tid":1945504,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"樓主一定好樣衰好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎人同我推佢落山<br />\n唔好俾佢個衰樣嚇親人</span></span>"},